Issue an Order granting the applicant&#8217;s request for certification by waiver to provide telecommunications services within the District of Columbia. Such certification shall specify whether the applicant is authorized to provide resold
        services, facilities-based services, or both. If a telecommunications service provider granted certification by waiver desires to provide services other than those permitted by the certification, the telecommunications service provider shall file
        another Application, with an additional application fee, requesting certification to provide those additional services;
